@startuml
actor User
participant server
database "user" as db

User ->> server : 1 POST /sign-up with body: email and password\nactivate server
server ->> db : 2 Check email existence\nactivate db

alt Email existed
    db --> server : 3 Error code\ndeactivate db
    server --> User : 4 Error message\nd deactivate server
    
else [Email is new]
    db --> server : 5 Email is available\ndeactivate db
    activate server 
    note right of server #D9E8F6#**Hashing Process**: \n- Generate salt\n- Apply hash function to (password + salt)\nnote end    
    loop Hash iterations
        Server <-Server:#Internal processing#\nend        
     alt Success? then Store data else Retry hashing endif     
